    "description": "System Research Co.,Ltd. provides software development services in Japan. The company designs, develops, implements, operates, maintains, and improves corporate information systems for the car, logistics, distribution, communication and control, and plant/line control industries. It also offers system integration; IT consulting; ICT infrastructure support for cloud implementation and server infrastructure, as well as PC environment planning, construction, and operation; ERP; and low-code development services. In addition, the company provides EC, business package, CRM/CTI, RPA, AI, document, BI and data analysis, data linkage, development platform, assessment services, PMO services, and infrastructure solutions. Further, it is involved in the creation, sale, distribution, and maintenance of programs; sale of personal computers, IT devices, and software products; document PDF + OCR conversion; operation and management of websites; provision of SaaS cloud and data entry services. System Research Co.,Ltd. was incorporated in 1981 and is headquartered in Nagoya, Japan."
